Prebuilt information extraction 
air-waybill-extraction-4.1.6 
An extractor model for air waybill (AWB). 
Release date 2024-06-11 
Available platforms Upstage Console 
Field descriptions 
Field Description Example value 
document_information.document_name Document Name Air Waybill 
document_infornation.air_waybil_number House Air Waybill Number EQEWSA202301001 
document_information.master_ai_vajol_number Master Air Waybill Number 999-21234530 
document_ information.executed_date Date of Issue 07-Nov-2018 
document_information.executed_place Place of Issue SAN FRANCISCO 
document_information.signatory_name Issuing Agent's Name (Name of Lucy Park 
the signatory at the bottom of 
the document) 
shipping_information.shipper_name Shipper's Name (The person or AHTWO CO.,LTD. 
company sending the goods) 
shipping information shipper_address Shipper's Address AMPEL PHAREM VILLAGE, VIHEA LOUNG COMMUNE, 
PUNHEA LUE DISTRICT, KANDAL, PROVINCE, CAMBODIA. 
shipping_informationshipper_phone_number Shipper's Telephone Number +82-31-777-8878
